         <OBJECT_CONTRACT ITEM="1">
            <TITLE>
               <P>Pre-Procurement, Market Engagement — Multi-disciplinary team for architecture and design services</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>CCS/18/024</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="71220000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The City and County of Swansea has published this Prior Information Notice (‘PIN’), as the Council is keen to give potential contractors an overview of the outline scope of work required, invite comments and provide clarity on the requirements.</P>
               <P>Potential bidders are invited to attend a Q&amp;A meeting with the Council team, at a mutually convenient time, and can visit the site if required. The meeting should last no more than an hour. Alternatively, a telephone call can be arranged.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
